extends layout

block content
  div
    div.row
      h3.col-sm-offset-3.col-sm-8.red #[strong Genetic Algorithm - Traveling Salesman] 
      p#description.col-sm-11.
        This is a solution to the traveling salesman problem (an NP-hard problem) using a genetic algorithm.  Coded in nodejs with data transmitted from an AWS server to your browser via Web Sockets (socket.io) and the visualization in HTML5 Canvas.  You can see even up to a 70-city graph, a solution is reached very quickly (given, say, you retain the default inputs I've placed with a mere 100 chromosomes in the population and a mutation rate of 9%).  You can get the code (and most of this site, actually), on#[a(href='https://github.com/cfsmrico/chaneyfonseca.net')  Github]
    div.row
      form.col-sm-3(ng-submit='runSim()', ng-controller='gatspController')
        div.row
          h4.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-4 #[strong Input]
        div.row
          label(for='nCities').h4.col-sm-6 # Cities
          input(type='number', min='10', max='100', name='nCities', ng-model='nCities', ng-init='nCities=40')#nCities.col-sm-4.ga-tsp
        div.row
          label(for='population').h4.col-sm-6 Population
          input(type='number', min='10', max='1000', name='population', ng-model='population', ng-init='population=100')#population.col-sm-4.ga-tsp
        div.row
          label(for='mutationPct').h4.col-sm-6 Mutation %
          input(type='number', min='0', max='100', name='mutationPct', ng-model='mutationPct', ng-init='mutationPct=9')#mutationPct.col-sm-4.ga-tsp
        div.row
          label(for='nGenerations').h4.col-sm-6 Generations
          input(type='number', min='100', max='9999', name='nGenerations', ng-model='nGenerations', ng-init='nGenerations=1000')#nGenerations.col-sm-4.ga-tsp
        div.row
          input(type='submit', value='GO!')#goButton.h4.col-sm-5
      div.col-sm-7
        div.row
          h4#result-text.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-4
            strong Result
        div.row
          canvas#tsp-graph.col-sm-12
        div.row#initial-gen-row
          h4#initial-text.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-4
            strong 
        div.row
          canvas#tsp-graph-g1.col-sm-12